Release Note 	: 1				Date 12/1/95


Product Name	: ASPIHDRM.SYS/EXE
Description	: ASPI Harddisk Driver for DOS
Version		: Ver 4.00
Release Date	: 12th January, 1995

Features:
		. Support for media with 1KB Sector size format

		. the "/L:X" (X - start drive letter) switch for specifying
		  the start drive letter ( only for ASPIHDRM.EXE)
		Usage:
		  ASPIHDRM /L:E
		  indicates to ASPIHDRM to assign drive letters starting from
		  'E'.

		. By default supports only Shuttle ASPI Managers. The "/ALL"
		switch is necessary for supporting third party partitions.
		Usage:
		  DEVICE = ASPIHDRM.SYS /ALL

